  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/notifications <action> --keys <key> - Fire action (reply, archive, etc.)
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/notifications cancel --keys <key|--all> - Dismiss
  NOTE: --keys mode uses stable identifiers that don't change; indices shift when notifications change

Media:
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/music <play|pause|toggle|next|prev|volume> - Control media

Volume:
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume list - List all streams with volume bars
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume <stream> - Show volume for stream
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume <stream> <N> - Set absolute volume
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume <stream> up [N] - Increment by N (default 1)
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume <stream> down [N] - Decrement by N (default 1)
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume up [N] - Increment music (default stream)
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/volume down [N] - Decrement music (default stream)
  Streams: alarm, call, music, notification, ring, system

System:
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/status - Battery, network, storage, memory, uptime
  ~/repos/termux-launcher-tools/update - Update tools from GitHub

Web Search:
